node.description:
Driver for UVC compatible webcams, which can also be used together with the Gumstix camera e-CAM32 OMAP GSTIX.

Driver uses v4l2 for direct configurations and GStreamer for image-requesting. DSP-accelerated jpeg-conversion is supported (see http://felipec.wordpress.com/tag/gstreamer/ for details).
